.Im MicroEmacs command|osd
.so me.tni
.TH major-mode-help 3
.XI major-mode-help - "Displays help page for current buffer"
.SH NAME
major-mode-help \- Displays help page for current buffer
.Me $a
.SH SYNOPSIS
.na
.B major-mode-help
.ad
.SH DESCRIPTION
\fBmajor-mode-help\fR  opens a dialog  giving  the user a brief  help  page on
tools available for the current buffer. The help page changes depending on the
type of the current buffer.
.SH HISTORY
\fBmajor-mode-help\fR  was  introduced in the 2006 release,  prior to this the
command was known as \fBbuffer-help\fR.
.SH "SEE ALSO"
.na
.Ht major-mode-setup 3 .
.ad
.FH
